│Nowhere is more loved than this treasured
place where joyous times are shared with
family, friends and all who stop to wonder al
the beauty surrounding them. Christine Kitchen."╣
ČIn loving memory of Elizabeth Teifer
Night Sister at the National Hospital from 1971 to 2007
Sadly missed by your family, friends and staff
of the National Hospital
Rest in Peace"╣
ČThis bench celebrates 21 years of Mothers For Peace
Thanks to our founders Lucy Behenna and Marion Mansergh
World peace will come through the will
